parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the windshield wipers can cause reduced visibility, leading to accidents, especially during rainy or humid weather conditions.
symptoms: The windshield wipers work intermittently
stop working altogether
make a loud buzzing noise
or fail to turn on
causing poor visibility while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake fade and pedal sinking can lead to extended stopping distances, increasing the risk of accidents, and potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
brakes fade after stopping at a light or on a hill
need to pump the brakes to get them to work
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS failure can cause the vehicle to lose traction, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities, especially on slippery or uneven road surfaces.
symptoms: The ABS warning light stays on
the vehicle does not stop when the brakes are applied
the brakes lock up
the vehicle skids or loses traction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Intermittent brake failure can lead to unpredictable stopping behavior, increasing the risk of accidents, and potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brakes fail intermittently
the brake pedal goes to the floor occasionally
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
the brakes work normally sometimes
but not always.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat frame can cause the seat to become unstable, leading to accidents or injuries, particularly during sudden stops or sharp turns.
symptoms: The seat rocks back and forth
the seat falls into the back seat
a popping noise is heard
the seat anchor separates from the metal frame
the frame crossmember is fractured.
